          "function_call": null,
          "function_response": null,
          "inline_data": null,
          "text": "Unfortunately, my system can only book one appointment at a time. To book a series of three meetings, we would need to book each one individually.\n\nWould you like to proceed with booking the first meeting, and then we can look for the subsequent two? We can aim for roughly one meeting per week as you requested.",
