          "text": "I appreciate the offer, but I really need to book the series of three together. It's important for my planning to have all three confirmed at once. The \"series of three investing meetings spread across the next month\" is a single request for me. Can you confirm if booking multiple, linked appointments like that is something your system is capable of, even if it means a different process?",
